name: The Lovers - 6 -
description: [ENG] - It doesn't necessarily talk about love and relationships. It represents opportunities, benefits and possible offers in your life right now. At the same time, free will and indecision can divide your opinion. This can make you doubtful about how to act on certain matters. [PT/BR] - Não fala necessariamente sobre amor e relacionamentos.
